{
  "stem": "5496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was able to tell him that I was with his mother just before she died.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But that's the only person that I met in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Funny, none-- it were just, it will end and I will be with my parents.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there was no elation, not even on the day of liberation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't say that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were not euphoric, and nobody was dancing in the street.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We either didn't have the strength or the stamina to do either.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The British came in, and they were extremely kind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They treated us like children and they were gentle and kind.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But as I said, there was no joy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was really too sick and emaciated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they took me, immediately, to near Bergen-Belsen to another place-- not where we worked, where the Germans used to live.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were in very clean and nice barracks, assigned to, like, five girls to one cubicle.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was clean and nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the girls would go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I was just-- I always try to analyze it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I must have been in a state of terrific depression, because I wouldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Even after the liberation, I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the girls were extremely nice.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they went out and got food and brought me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I was just lying there, I remember, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for a long, long period of time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I just wouldn't take any nourishment, afterwards.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was always hoping to see my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in fact, I never forget, one kind British soldier came, and he brought us stuff.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he gave me a box of sardines.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[CRYING] And my sister was very fond of sardines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I hid it, to bring it home for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
